    "16017": "Solution Tip",
    "16018": "One of the stair's tread profiles overlaps more than one other profiles in the same direction.",
    "16019": "Modify the tread profiles so that each except the first and last either overlaps or intersects with the profiles immediately above and below it in the stair path, and so that no tread profile overlaps more than one other profile in the same direction.",
